# opena2a review demo
Output docs/images/review-demo.gif

Set Width 900
Set Height 450
Set FontSize 16
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 15

Hide
Type "cd /Users/ecolibria/workspace/opena2a-org/test/hma && clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "npx opena2a-cli review --ci"
Enter
Sleep 6s

Sleep 4s
